Introduction

Seolhyun (설현) is a South Korean singer and actress signed under IEUM HASHTAG. She is a former member of AOA. Seolhyun has gradually gained popularity through various television series, acts, and endorsements.

In 2010, Seolhyun won the 8th Smart Model Contest where she was later scouted by FNC Entertainment. On July 16, 2012, Seolhyun was revealed as a member of AOA, and later debuted with the group on July 30, with the song "Elvis" on Mnet's M Countdown.

On October 20, 2022, it was announced that Seolhyun would part ways from FNC Entertainment after 10 years. Seolhyun later signed with IEUM HASHTAG in November.
